== Data Setup

rake db:reset; rake sunspot:reindex

== ERD Generator

railroad -M | neato -Tpng > app/assets/images/models.png

== Notes on Stack, Dependencies

- nginx + passenger
- authentication: devise
- authorization: acl9
- ajax-upload tool: plupload
- search: solr, sunspot
- tagging: acts_as_taggable_on 
- javascript lib: jQuery, jQuery UI
- pagination: will_paginate
- file metadata: fits
- background jobs: resque + redis

== TESTING

 - config/database.yml must have test database defined
 - unit testing with RSpec (rake spec)
 - code coverage reports with RCov (rake rcov:rspec, then see http://<your_camp>/coverage/index.html)
